headline: Mizuho upgrades Prologis, sees room for stock to recover in coming months
summary: Investing.com -- Mizuho upgraded Prologis (NYSE:PLD) to Outperform from Neutral, saying the industrial REIT is set up for tactical outperformance over the next six months after lagging peers recently.
